title: Live updates: ASX set to tumble 1.3pc as disappointing US jobs data sends Wall Street tumbling
description: The ASX is set to drop 1.3pc on opening following a rough session on Wall Street where disappointing jobs data undermined hopes for a soft economic landing. Follow the day's events and insights from our business reporters on the ABC News live markets blog.
